&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 5 Pre Assessment Nurse&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a self- motivated RN to join our pre-assessment team at BHRUT. An understanding of pre-assessment and would be an advantage. The successful applicant will need to demonstrate a willingness to learn and develop to deliver nurse led clinics They will be highly motivated to provide a high quality service and be flexible to meet the needs of the service&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For any informal enquires please contact Linda Covell, Matron, Tel: 01708 435 000 EXT 5111 and email: Linda.covell@nhs.net.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All new staff appointed to posts at the Trust is subject to a probationary period. This will give the new staff member an opportunity to become familiar with the culture and working environment of the Trust&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applications should be made online, however, queries regarding the application process or assistance with completion of the form (for applicants with a disability) can be made to Nadeem Arif, Recruitment Advisor, on 01708 435000 ext. 2289. Further details regarding the post may be obtained by contacting the manager as per the contact details above.&lt;/p&gt;
